title_bed_bats_review: Boutique hotel in Kolatoli, Cox's Bazar · 1 bedroom · 2 beds · 1 private bath
listing_description: You'll enjoy your time at this cheerful getaway in Cox's Bazar. Enjoy easy access to popular tourist destinations and restaurants from this charming place to stay. Featuring a bar, Windy Terrace Boutique Hotel is located in Cox's Bazar. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a 24-hour front desk and room service, along with free WiFi. The property has an ATM and a concierge service for guests. The accommodation offers a continental or Asian breakfast.

title_bed_bats_review: Hotel in Cox's Bazar · 2 bedrooms · 2 beds · 2 baths
listing_description:
Hotel The Cox Today is a privately owned 5 Star Standard Luxury Hotel in Cox's Bazar, Bangladesh. It is situated in an attractive location of Kolatoli Road, Cox's Bazar which is only 5 minutes drive form the Cox's Bazar Airport. It is a place of choice of most of the corporate executives, foreigners  and for those who prefer to stay in luxury with stunning view of The 'Bay of Bengal'.
Complimentary: buffet breakfast, swimming pool, gym and airport pick-up & drop service.
